{{#titleicon_unicode:💵}}
Pages in this category are individual income entries created via
[[Form:Income]] (or directly through the form-edit flow from
[[Special:ReceiptReview]]).

For totals, filtering, and CSV export across all entries, use
[[Special:Ledger|the ledger]].

The <code>{{#titleicon_unicode:}}</code> call above sets the title icon
for every page in this category — [[Template:Income]] auto-categorizes
income pages here. Change the emoji here to retheme all income entries
at once. Requires the [[mw:Extension:TitleIcon|TitleIcon]] extension.
